assets.description:
Green is always the first color on my mind. Living in the North East of the US (Boston) it is the first green seedlings sprouting in the spring. In VR, colors are often very saturated and bright so I am challenging myself to paint subtle, soothing environments that could become places of retreat just like a garden. 
#TiltbrushPaintOff2021 #punktvr
